title: Zina Sterling Silver Palm Springs Clip Earrings
description:
Inspired by the richness of Palm Springs design, Zina Sterling Silver reimagines bold elements of Midcentury Modern into a glamorous new jewelry collection. The Clip Earrings strike a balance of elegance with simplicity, perfect to wear from day to night. Made of sterling silver. Cast, finished, and polished by hand in USA.

  • Dimensions: .75 x .25 x 1 in.
